| Average test CTR | >2% | Across all variants |
| CPA reduction (30-day) | -25% | Compared to baseline |
| CPA reduction (90-day) | -50% | Compared to baseline |
| Conversion rate lift | 2–10× | Landing page or funnel conversion rate |
| Comment-to-Coin ratio | >10% | % of mined comments that become Gold Coins |
| Cost per Sprint Test | ≤$35 | Ad spend per test cycle |

